dict.string: The engines busily hauled logs and shunted flatbeds. But when they came to a rickety old bridge, Thomas stopped. Thomas didn’t like the bridge, but he knew he had to cross it to collect the jobi wood. So, wobbly wheel by wobbly wheel, he crept slowly across.
